          "reviewBody": "It is one of the best and reputed schools in Kolkata. I have been studying there for the last 11 years and the teachers are so good. The best teachers are Tania Mukherjee Seal ma'am (History), Sushma Shaw ma'am (Hindi), Ahana ma'am ( Physics)",
