          },
          "datePublished": "2023-04-24",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I would like to offer a sincere piece of advice to parents: be cautious of certain schools(especially this one) that use manipulative marketing tactics to lure you in. Despite their claims of being the best school with a positive learning environment, they may not actually live up to those standards. It's important to note that they didn't even have a system in place for receiving feedback. Additionally, the teachers and staff can be disrespectful towards parents. The school's owner is a large corporation, which may explain their arrogant behavior and willingness to deceive and mistreat parents without any remorse. This school is striving to be seen as an elite institution, yet they are not genuinely concerned about the majority of their students and show favoritism",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
