            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Ok so i have been waiting to write an honest review.\nWhats in the name.\nThe so called inclusive dept is just for the name sake.\nTeachers are not at all co operative\ntowards delayed students..\nThey cant even handle a crying child. Very bad experience i had.\nWaste of time, money and my son's development detoriated just because of there ignorance and no co operation. He was traumatized to see this school..\nI had many hopes from this institute. But i wasted my time here.\nA big no for special needs.\nThe condition might worsten in such environment",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
